{"tid":2322591,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"南柱赫箍牙前照片曝光！進化效果堪比整容","createTime":"2020-12-12T12:11:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-13T00:59:03.000Z","uid":3189,"like":15,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"0f4fe02399356805dd8e0a974254b21e5fd0caa2","tid":2322591,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T12:11:33.000Z","msg":"韓星南柱赫在《奶酪陷阱》嶄露頭角，成為了新一代炙手可熱的「小鮮肉」，開始慢慢受到人們所熟知。近年更在多部電視劇擔任要角，如《學校2015》、《舉重妖精金福珠》等，人氣一時勢如破竹。不過身材高挑、外貌出眾的男神早前就宣佈和李聖經蜜運，令到不少粉絲都嘆夢中情人已有愛人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.popnews.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/d2578880.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.popnews.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2Fd2578880.jpg&h=f28f3c84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_a3ac160cdef69300d909d2acf356d269/static.koreastardaily.com/2018-09-20/109508-657164.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_a3ac160cdef69300d909d2acf356d269%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2018-09-20%2F109508-657164.png&h=c9f77e39&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但原來男神並非一朝一夕可煉成，近日韓網瘋傳南柱赫的國小、國中畢業照，從照片中可見南柱赫小時候臉型明顯和現在有極大的差別。國小和國中時的南柱赫仍然見到招牌單眼皮和英氣的眉毛，不過合嘴時的牙齒部分還是相當的突出，「暴牙」的問題似乎頗為嚴重。再加上又短又厚的瀏海造型，完全和「男神」二未沾不上邊。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_ca33aa1fe6a65615db43b13978ba8c8c/static.koreastardaily.com/2018-09-20/109508-657162.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_ca33aa1fe6a65615db43b13978ba8c8c%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2018-09-20%2F109508-657162.png&h=3013445a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.popnews.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/1497082915_843d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.popnews.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F1497082915_843d.jpg&h=95817bac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過後來南柱赫高中時戴上牙套矯正牙齒，臉型亦都變成瓜子臉，到高中拍畢業照時，儼然已經是個長相秀氣的男生。由國小到高中樣甩的轉變堪比整容，令不少網友驚訝。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hips.hearstapps.com/hmg-prod.s3.amazonaws.com/images/n2ljj-1602832451.jpg?crop=0.307xw:0.613xh;0.0180xw,0&amp;resize=640:*\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhips.hearstapps.com%2Fhmg-prod.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fimages%2Fn2ljj-1602832451.jpg%3Fcrop%3D0.307xw%3A0.613xh%3B0.0180xw%2C0%26resize%3D640%3A%2A&h=2a0a8a5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://dw6vrgax4fzym.cloudfront.net/userfiles/sm/sm1200_images_A1/9278/2016111406041480.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdw6vrgax4fzym.cloudfront.net%2Fuserfiles%2Fsm%2Fsm1200_images_A1%2F9278%2F2016111406041480.jpg&h=cd82b3a3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"41e953330ac1917a9395200a5f8ef81b5f89c04a","tid":2322591,"uid":12469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f4fe02399356805dd8e0a974254b21e5fd0caa2","tid":2322591,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T12:11:33.000Z","msg":"韓星南柱赫在《奶酪陷阱》嶄露頭角，成為了新一代炙手可熱的「小鮮肉」，開始慢慢受到人們所熟知。近年更在多部電視劇擔任要角，如《學校2015》、《舉重妖精金福珠》等，人氣一時勢如破竹。不過身材高挑、外貌出眾的男神早前就宣佈和李聖經蜜運，令到不少粉絲都嘆夢中情人已有愛人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.popnews.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/d2578880.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.popnews.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2Fd2578880.jpg&h=f28f3c84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_a3ac160cdef69300d909d2acf356d269/static.koreastardaily.com/2018-09-20/109508-657164.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_a3ac160cdef69300d909d2acf356d269%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2018-09-20%2F109508-657164.png&h=c9f77e39&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但原來男神並非一朝一夕可煉成，近日韓網瘋傳南柱赫的國小、國中畢業照，從照片中可見南柱赫小時候臉型明顯和現在有極大的差別。國小和國中時的南柱赫仍然見到招牌單眼皮和英氣的眉毛，不過合嘴時的牙齒部分還是相當的突出，「暴牙」的問題似乎頗為嚴重。再加上又短又厚的瀏海造型，完全和「男神」二未沾不上邊。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_ca33aa1fe6a65615db43b13978ba8c8c/static.koreastardaily.com/2018-09-20/109508-657162.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\